OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FPublic health authorities across the
OL,8,FChannel Islands are asking children
OL,9,Fand young adults to check they have
OL,10,Fbeen properly vaccinated against
OL,11,Fmeningitis.
OL,13,FIt comes after the number of
OL,14,Fmeningitis B cases identified as part
OL,15,Fof a recent outbreak in Kent has now
OL,16,Frisen to 20.
OL,18,FMeningitis is an infection of the
OL,19,Fmembranes surrounding the brain and
OL,20,Fspinal cord caused either by a
OL,21,Fbacterial or viral infection.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FWhilst the condition can affect
OL,8,Fanyone, it is more common in children
OL,9,Fand young adults.
OL,11,FTwo students from Kent have died from
OL,12,Fthe infection, and several more are in
OL,13,Fserious condition in hospital -
OL,14,Fprompting the UK Government to launch
OL,15,Fa 'targeted' vaccine rollout scheme in
OL,16,Fthe area.
OL,18,FIn both Guernsey and Jersey, the
OL,19,FMenACWY vaccine is available free of
OL,20,Fcharge for anyone up to the age of 25.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThis vaccine is typically administered
OL,8,Fby school nurses, and protects against
OL,9,Fthe 'ACWY' strains of the
OL,10,Fmeningococcal disease - which cause
OL,11,Fboth meningitis and septicaemia.
OL,13,FThere is also a specific meningitis B
OL,14,Fvaccination that was introduced as
OL,15,Fpart of the baby and pre-school
OL,16,Froutine vaccination schedule in 2015.
OL,18,FIslanders can check their vaccination
OL,19,Fstatus with their GPs or the
OL,20,FImmunisation Teams.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
