CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FWhat are the symptoms of meningitis?
OL,9,FMeningitis can initially resemble flu
OL,10,For a bad hangover. Its symptoms
OL,11,Fdevelop suddenly, and can include:
OL,13,FThe symptoms can appear in any order,
OL,14,Fand patients do not always get all the
OL,15,Fsymptoms.
OL,17,FIf left untreated, the illness can
OL,18,Fbecome incredibly serious.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FIf someone is concerned about possible
OL,8,Fmeningitis symptoms, they should seek
OL,9,Furgent medical advice from the
OL,10,Femergency department.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Professor Peter
OL,13,FBradley, Jersey's Director of Public
OL,14,FHealth, said: "While we are aware of
OL,15,Fthe meningitis cases reported in Kent,
OL,16,Fthe risk to islanders remains very low.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"Jersey continues to have good
OL,8,Fvaccination rates among children and
OL,9,Fyoung people, which provides strong
OL,10,Fprotection against a range of serious
OL,11,Fillnesses, including meningococcal
OL,12,Fdisease.
OL,14,F"We strongly encourage teenagers and
OL,15,Fyoung adults to ensure they are up to
OL,16,Fdate with their meningitis
OL,17,Fvaccinations, including the free
OL,18,FMenACWY vaccine available locally up
OL,19,Fto the age of 25.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"It is important that young people
OL,8,Fremain vigilant to the symptoms of
OL,9,Fmeningitis and seek urgent medical
OL,10,Fhelp if they have any concerns."
OL,12,FThe outbreak in Kent is being managed
OL,13,Fby the UK Health Security Agency
OL,14,F(UKHSA).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773846665
OL,3,CChannel Islanders urged to check
OL,4,Cvaccines amidst Kent meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FStudents from the Channel Islands who
OL,8,Fmight be studying in the area - and
OL,9,Fparticularly anyone studying at the
OL,10,FUniversity of Kent, where the outbreak
OL,11,Fhas been most serious - are being
OL,12,Fasked by the islands' public health
OL,13,Fauthorities to follow advice issued by
OL,14,Fthe UKHSA, their university, and local
OL,15,Fhealth services.
OL,17,FThey are also asked to attend any
OL,18,Fclinics if they are identified as
OL,19,Fcontacts of the existing cases, and
OL,20,Ftake full courses of antibiotics if
OL,21,Foffered.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
